msgid "Puṭṭho kho pana pañhābhinīto hāpetvā lambitvā aparipūraṃ avitthārena parassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti. "
msgstr "But when led on by questions they speak well of another without giving the full details, leaving many things out. "

msgctxt "an4.73:2.3"
msgid "Veditabbametaṃ, bhikkhave, asappuriso ayaṃ bhavanti. "
msgstr "That’s how to know that this is a bad person. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
