#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an4.73:9.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, vadhukā yaññadeva rattiṃ vā divaṃ vā ānītā hoti, tāvadevassā tibbaṃ hirottappaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti sassuyāpi sasurepi sāmikepi antamaso dāsakammakaraporisesu. "
msgstr "It’s like a bride on the day or night she’s first brought to her husband’s home. Right away she sets up a keen sense of conscience and prudence for her mother and father in law, her husband, and even the bondservants, workers, and staff. "

msgctxt "an4.73:9.2"
msgid "Sā aparena samayena saṃvāsamanvāya vissāsamanvāya sassumpi sasurampi sāmikampi evamāha: "
msgstr "But after some time, because of living together and familiarity, she’ll even say to her mother and father in law, or to her husband: "

msgctxt "an4.73:9.3"
msgid "‘apetha, kiṃ pana tumhe jānāthā’ti. "
msgstr "‘Go away! What would you know?’ "

msgctxt "an4.73:9.4"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhikkhu yaññadeva rattiṃ vā divaṃ vā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito hoti, tāvadevassa tibbaṃ hirottappaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti bhikkhūsu bhikkhunīsu upāsakesu upāsikāsu antamaso ārāmikasamaṇuddesesu. "
msgstr "In the same way, on the day or night a mendicant first goes forth from the lay life to homelessness, right away they set up a keen sense of conscience and prudence for the monks, nuns, laymen, and laywomen, and even the monastery workers and novices. "

msgctxt "an4.73:9.5"
msgid "So aparena samayena saṃvāsamanvāya vissāsamanvāya ācariyampi upajjhāyampi evamāha: "
msgstr "But after some time, because of living together and familiarity, they’ll even say to their teacher or mentor: "

msgctxt "an4.73:9.6"
msgid "‘apetha, kiṃ pana tumhe jānāthā’ti. "
msgstr "‘Go away! What would you know?’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.73:9.7"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "an4.73:9.8"
msgid "‘adhunāgatavadhukāsamena cetasā viharissāmā’ti. "
msgstr "‘We will live with hearts like that of a newly wedded bride.’ "

msgctxt "an4.73:9.9"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.73:9.10"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

